organic.title: Pediatric Gastroenterology | The Children's Hospital at Providence
organic.snippet: The Pediatric Gastroenterology team at Children's Hospital at Providence treats a wide range of GI and liver conditions in children and adolescents.

organic.title: Pediatric Gastroenterology - Providence
organic.snippet: We specialize in problems of the esophagus, gallbladder, intestines, liver, pancreas and stomach in children and adolescents.

organic.title: Umran Senyer, MD | Anchorage, AK - Providence
organic.snippet: Dr. Senyer is a board-certified pediatric gastroenterologist and an active North American Society of Pediatric Gastroenterology Hepatology and Nutrition member.

organic.title: Pediatric Subspecialties Clinic | Providence Medical Group
organic.snippet: The Pediatric Subspecialty Clinic at Providence Health in Anchorage provides expert, personalized care for children with a wide range of conditions.
